project_descr: By addressing issues pertaining to  governance, civil service reintegration, improving local  capacities and planning schemes, as well as  the social cohesion of Palestinian society, the project aims to strengthen Palestinian National Unity.

outputs.output_descr: The project aimes at anchoring national unity and social cohesion throughout the Palestinian society through support to consolidated governance mechanisms, social reconciliation, & enhanced civic engagement.
